2.3.2 - 2013-12-03
 - Added new functionality to add ticket types and services as send conditions for the survey.

2.3.1 - 2013-11-12
 - Fixed Bug#9757 - Back buttons should to lead to last used screen and not browser history back.
 - Made survey zoom menu flexible (by SysConfig settings)
 - Improved Survey Overview visuals
 - Added Answer Required column to questions overview.
 - Added Simplified Chinese translation thanx to Michael Shi!

2.2.91 - 2013-09-24
 - Initial release for OTRS 3.3.x series.
 - Added Malaysia translation, thanks to Kenny Cheah.
 - Added Japanese translation, thanks to Norihiro Tanaka.
 - Fixed bug#9544 thanx to Daniel Santos!
 - Extended unittests to check for Survey link mangling during sending process.
 - Improved graphical columns usability
 - Changed API:
     SurveyNew()       => SurveyAdd()
     SurveySave()      => SurveyUpdate()
     SurveyQueueSave() => SurveyQueueSet()
     AnswerSave        => AnswerUpdate()
     PublicAnswerSave  => PublicAnswerSet()
     CountRequest      => RequestCount()
     CountVote         => VoteCount()
 - Split Frontend module AgentSurvey.pm
 - Improved error screens

